----
++ ADDENDUM 3739.1
+++ EXPERIMENTATION LOG
----
[[/div]]

Site-82's Memetics Research Group C mail-ordered [[span class="moo"]]Moosphere[[/span]] company products for testing. Researchers selected [[span class="moo choco"]]Chocolate Mind-Milk™[[/span]] due to its popularity and unique production process. Testing occurred with the goal of understanding [[span class="moo"]]Moosphere[[/span]]'s use of literary archetypes in marketing, manufacturing, and product sales.

Each [[span class="moo choco"]]Chocolate Mind-Milk™[[/span]] packaging contained[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]Alongside a dairy-based pun on the carton inset.[[/span]] the text "What was your [[span class="moo"]]Mind-Milk™[[/span]] experience like?" with an attached phone number. Researchers consumed the product daily (before a full night's rest) over a 10-day period. Personnel noted any recurring dreams or motifs in a Standard Dream Report before relaying them to the phone line.

Within two to five business days, each of the researchers encountered the following archetypal representations:

||||~ Archetype 01: Trickster||
||~ Moosphere expression||Outreach Specialists||
||~ Moosphere manifestation||[[span class="moo"]]Moosphere[[/span]] mascot "Jackie the Clown Cow" (**SCP-3739-1-A**) appeared to researchers. Subject possessed a lean bovine appearance and wore a mask resembling a fennec fox. Subject danced in the air, emitting bovine vocalizations and showering researchers in soy milk.||
||||~ Archetype 07: Mother||
||~ Moosphere expression||Mammary Mothers||
||~ Moosphere manifestation||See Addendum 3739.4.||
||||~ Archetype 08: Wounded Child||
||~ Moosphere expression||Child Curdles/Coagulated Children||
||~ Moosphere manifestation||A group of 15 "Child Curdles" (**SCP-3739-1-C**) appeared at the Research Group Supervisor's home at 4:07 AM. All subjects had varying levels of injuries and appeared as golden age animated cartoon characters.[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]Hand-drawn, rubber hose animation dating back to the 1920s.[[/span]] One of the instances, self-identifying as "Creamy Charlie", recounted dairy-themed parables at 90 decibels. Most notably, the Supervisor's daughter, age 7, was diagnosed with hypocalcemia[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]**hypocalcemia:** A medical condition wherein a patient has too little calcium in the blood.[[/span]] three weeks prior.||
||||~ Archetype 14: The Flood||
||~ Moosphere expression||{{N/A}}||
||~ Moosphere manifestation||Researcher Mathias dreamt of a biblical flood sending tsunamis of milk into population centers. Upon reporting the motif to the phone line, an automated voice said "Please hold" before expelling milk from the receiver at 1 L/minute. This ended after five minutes when Mathias severed the phone line. Dream aligns with designated MF-Class "Spilled Milk" Scenario on the catastrophe classification list.||

[[div class="lite-heading"]]
----
++ ADDENDUM 3739.2
+++ HISTORY, DISCOVERY, AND RECOVERY
----
[[/div]]

[[include :scp-wiki:component:image-features-source |hover-enlarge=--]
